If errors on clone from github, execute this command in both the Api and Data Project

dotnet add package Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Sqlite



full order of commands steps:
-----------------------------
cd Chrome.Stallion.Api
dotnet add package Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Sqlite
cd ..
cd Chrome.Stallion.Data
dotnet add package Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Sqlite


Info on Swagger:
-----------------------------
Run through the Run and Debug menu
copy url of local host port that it opens in browser

add swagger end of URL part as shown below:
https://localhost:(your port number)/swagger/index.html

^You need the REST CLIENT extension for all this stuff but you should have that by now

